 dissection. <em>Ann Cardiothorac Surg</em> 2016;5(4):275–295.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.21037/acs.2016.05.05">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27563541/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Evolution+of+surgical+therapy+for+Stanford+acute+type+A+aortic+dissection&amp;author=P+Chiu&amp;author=DC+Miller&amp;publication_year=2016&amp;journal=Ann+Cardiothorac+Surg&amp;pages=275-295&amp;doi=10.21037%2Facs.2016.05.05&amp;pmid=27563541">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">4.</div><div id="r4" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Daily PO, Trueblood HW, Stinson EB, et al. Management of acute aortic dissections. <em>Ann Thorac Surg</em> 1970;10(3):237–247.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/S0003-4975(10)65594-4">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/5458238/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Management+of+acute+aortic+dissections&amp;author=PO+Daily&amp;author=HW+Trueblood&amp;author=EB+Stinson&amp;publication_year=1970&amp;journal=Ann+Thorac+Surg&amp;pages=237-247&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0003-4975%2810%2965594-4&amp;pmid=5458238">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">DeBakey ME, McCollum CH, Crawford ES, et al. Dissection and dissecting aneurysms of the aorta: twenty-year follow-up of 527 patients treated surgically. <em>Surgery</em> 1982;92(6):1118–1134.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7147190/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Dissection+and+dissecting+aneurysms+of+the+aorta%3A+twenty-year+follow-up+of+527+patients+treated+surgically&amp;author=ME+DeBakey&amp;author=CH+McCollum&amp;author=ES+Crawford&amp;publication_year=1982&amp;journal=Surgery&amp;pages=1118-1134&amp;pmid=7147190">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Dake MD, Thompson M, van Sambeek M, et al. DISSECT: a new mnemonic-based approach to the categorization of aortic dissection. <em>Eur J Vasc Endovasc Surg</em> 2013;46(2):175–190.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ejvs.2013.04.029">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23721817/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=DISSECT%3A+a+new+mnemonic-based+approach+to+the+categorization+of+aortic+dissection&amp;author=MD+Dake&amp;author=M+Thompson&amp;author=M+van+Sambeek&amp;publication_year=2013&amp;journal=Eur+J+Vasc+Endovasc+Surg&amp;pages=175-190&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.ejvs.2013.04.029&amp;pmid=23721817">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Clough RE, Waltham M, Giese D, Taylor PR, Schaeffter T. A new imaging method for assessment of aortic dissection using four-dimensional phase contrast magnetic resonance imaging. <em>J Vasc Surg</em> 2012;55(4):914–923.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jvs.2011.11.005">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="http